### What happened

When I clicked the button to copy a process, the prompt was incorrect. I've checked the codes about it and the correct prompt should be '不支持复制的任务类型[....]'.

![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4928204/148062092-a7d415dc-22f4-4ce3-867b-2b101ece0422.png)


### What you expected to happen

I expect that there will be a correct prompt when I use the function of copying process.

### How to reproduce

By now the function of copying process has never supported the process that contains any switch type tasks. So  when clicking the process contains a switch type task , the system will prompt the correct cause.
